      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST QUICKLY (3) goes very well here starting seven times for three wins and two minors. In the money last time at Bendigo (24.45) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5, finishing a 3 length third. Expected to be in the finish. IT'S SOYSAGES (2) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 three back then placing at Warrnambool before missing the frame latest when fourth (22.80) at this track. Expected to bounce back to best. ZIPPING SCOOBY (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Geelong behind Holyfield Chic (22.91) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Leading chance. ARGYLE EMMA (8) was in the money last start despite a big quote and is likely to feature again.",
